snippet.title: The Real Faces of VTuber｜Teaser Trailer｜PC Steam
snippet.description:
"Catch me if you can!"

"The Real Faces of VTuber" is a detective-genre visual novel where players act as a prosecutor investigating a murder at a VTuber agency, with the identity of the Nakanohito being key to solving the case.

WISHLIST & FOLLOW to get notified when the game launches! 
https://reurl.cc/54jj4G

Follow us on social media!
https://twitter.com/liliengames

Trailer:Marcy
Music:甘茶の音楽工房
